description: Claritas, LLC is a data-driven marketing company that helps brands target and engage their ideal audiences. Using its proprietary AI engine and an identity graph that tracks over 255 million consumers, the firm provides predictive demographics, multichannel measurement, and identity resolution to improve marketing ROI.
